import React, { Component } from 'react';
import { Nav, NavDropdown } from 'react-bootstrap';
import '../styles/CategoryMenu.css';

class CatagoryMenu extends Component {

	render() {
		return (
			<Nav justify defaultActiveKey="/home" as="ul" className="itemDropnList">
				<NavDropdown title="Clothing" id="nav-dropdown">
					<NavDropdown.Item eventKey="4.1">Tops</NavDropdown.Item>
					<NavDropdown.Item eventKey="4.2">Bottoms</NavDropdown.Item>
					<NavDropdown.Item eventKey="4.3">Dress</NavDropdown.Item>
				</NavDropdown>

				<NavDropdown title="SportWear" id="nav-dropdown">
					<NavDropdown.Item eventKey="4.1">Tops</NavDropdown.Item>
					<NavDropdown.Item eventKey="4.2">Bottoms</NavDropdown.Item>
					<NavDropdown.Item eventKey="4.3">Dress</NavDropdown.Item>
				</NavDropdown>

				<NavDropdown title="Outerwear" id="nav-dropdown">
					<NavDropdown.Item eventKey="4.1">Tops</NavDropdown.Item>
					<NavDropdown.Item eventKey="4.2">Bottoms</NavDropdown.Item>
					<NavDropdown.Item eventKey="4.3">Dress</NavDropdown.Item>
				</NavDropdown>

				<NavDropdown title="Clothing" id="nav-dropdown">
					<NavDropdown.Item eventKey="4.1">Tops</NavDropdown.Item>
					<NavDropdown.Item eventKey="4.2">Bottoms</NavDropdown.Item>
					<NavDropdown.Item eventKey="4.3">Dress</NavDropdown.Item>
				</NavDropdown>

				<NavDropdown title="Clothing" id="nav-dropdown">
					<NavDropdown.Item eventKey="4.1">Tops</NavDropdown.Item>
					<NavDropdown.Item eventKey="4.2">Bottoms</NavDropdown.Item>
					<NavDropdown.Item eventKey="4.3">Dress</NavDropdown.Item>
				</NavDropdown>
			</Nav>
		);
	}
}

export default CatagoryMenu;
